{"tid":1976830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[你分到幾多?] 第一輪防疫抗疫基金，庫房支出總數達2,875億，佔GDP約10%","createTime":"2020-04-17T13:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T17:52:19.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f2df0ca820c3f5653bbafc6ce2a2abde8df47d28","tid":1976830,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">政府公布第二輪防疫抗疫基金，林鄭表示整套措施的開支總額為1,375億，包括防疫抗疫基金另外注入1,095億、綜援額外動用32億等。而連同早前的《財政預算案》、第一輪防疫抗疫基金等，庫房支出總數達2,875億，佔GDP約10%。林鄭表示，預料今個年度的財政赤字由原本的1,391億擴大至2,766億，即是由GDP的4.8%增至9.5%。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2,875億 / 700萬=平均每人4萬1蚊<br />\n你分到幾多錢?"},{"pid":"1d89c97c6eecc5a8751c40aeb7c3864aca507628","tid":1976830,"uid":142676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:38:04.000Z","msg":"0"},{"pid":"5306dceede0f4c78974d9d27b932000e1d388203","tid":1976830,"uid":155137,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:54:31.000Z","msg":"負數 分唔到之餘仲要食佢派俾企業之後嘅通脹"},{"pid":"5f94002aa136b2e395330321eaeb3937099229ab","tid":1976830,"uid":246023,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"利益輸送為主架姐<br />\n大部份都流唔到入市民袋"},{"pid":"7013d5170cac22924862b0824df5d0cdbb625b88","tid":1976830,"uid":198595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T14:01:29.000Z","msg":"0..."},{"pid":"0c7bea6d21634c2734b52c80c2e21cd29f8cb765","tid":1976830,"uid":259010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T02:10:51.000Z","msg":"1萬 （可能等幾年）"},{"pid":"e0acdd061e6b2b5e414451852c0cfd0cd6376c90","tid":1976830,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOM8iHp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOM8iHp.jpg&h=e2f2e232&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb8922c7ab7d04f7dc9fa59dab77381661bb325d","tid":1976830,"uid":34047,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"c